<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Validate_Date currently requires an input format of YYYY-MM-DD, such as 2007-03-17. In the spirit of flexibility, the validation class should accept various other formats. Further, it should make use of Zend_Date, for DRYer code.</p>

<p>Priority minor since it is trivial to preformat a date such that it follows the YYYY-MM-DD format.</p>

